features: ** FEATURES ** Features a cup holder that fits most baby bottles, sippy cups and drinks. The snack compartment was ergonomically designed to be easy for the child to grasp and reach their food and snacks inside

** NON SKID SILICONE ARMS ** Best Stroller Connector! Our patented design silicone arms are flexible and easy to mount onto ANY stroller bar. With a true universal fit, it coils and grips the bar and stays in place. Remains upright and will not slip or slide.

** UNIVERSAL ** This universal snack tray for stroller is compatible with: Uppababy Vista V2, Nuna, MaxiCosi, Bugaboo, Graco, Britax, GB Pockit, Bob, Mompush, Baby Jogger City Tour 2, Baby Jogger City Mini G2, Chicco and more...

** EASY TO CLEAN ** This easy clean stroller tray attachment universal was designed for little kids and big messes. For small messes, just wipe clean, or rinse with warm soapy water. For a deeper cleanse, wash it in the dishwasher on the top rack. Wash as Instructed

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a great little universal snack tray. The flexible arms attach to the tray very easily. Once attached, you can wind them around pretty much anything. I have the TBG x Veer Switchback Off-Road Stroller. This wound easily around the bumper bar and stayed in place well. It's been SO nice being able to take a sippy cup and some light snacks on our morning walks. I think this is of great value and is a great option for anyone who doesn't want to splurge on a pricy name brand attachment.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My Chicco stroller has no tray and no attachments. I have tried several tray attachments and none have worked. This tray attachment is as close to perfect as I could get until my 19 mth old figured out that if she keeps turning the tray, it eventually comes off. Luckily as long as there are snacks or water bottle in it, she leaves it alone. Other times I store below.Overall, this is a really great snack tray. Very simple to put on and it stays in place when filled. I really like that the compartments are deep enough to keep the bottle and food in without being so deep she can’t get to them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very useful snack tray
reviews.reviewText: Not every stroller comes with a snack tray. We use a baby jogger city troll 2 stroller. Though it is excellent in being compact when folded, it lacks in storage space and does not have a snack tray. I was looking to add a snack try and came across this product. What I like is the snake-like wire mount. It reminds me of those stroller fans or camera tripods with the snake-like wire legs. You basically wrap it around any bar and it will hold. In contrast, others uses a clip on mount. I feel the snake-like mount is more sturdy and can be adjusted more. With a snack tray in place, I can have a place to hold my daughter's sippy cup and an area to place her snacks. I really like this accessory!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to attach, holds strong and my kiddo loves having easy access to his snacks and water.
reviews.reviewText: When our little one is in his stroller, he can get frustrated when his water or snacks are in his lap while we are driving around. This results in many dropped cups and snacks when they are not easy to get to.This snack tray is perfect for those strollers that don’t come with one like our Evenflo Gold Self-Folding Stroller.The tray was easy to attach and after I put some weight in it, it didn’t move. It is easy to take off and clean and no issues getting or little one in and out of the stroller with it attached.Our toddler is very happy to have his drink and snacks within his reach.
